article.description: Azar Swain had 21 points as Yale defeated Dartmouth 75-57 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Swain scores 21 to carry Yale past Dartmouth 75-57
article.linkText: Swain scores 21 to carry Yale past Dartmouth 75-57
article.story: NEW HAVEN, Conn. -- Azar Swain had 21 points as Yale defeated Dartmouth 75-57 on Saturday night. Paul Atkinson had 17 points and eight rebounds for Yale (17-5, 5-1 Ivy League). Wyatt Yess added 11 points and seven rebounds. Eric Monroe had eight assists. Chris Knight had 12 points for the Big Green (7-14, 0-6), who have now lost nine games in a row. James Foye added 11 points. Yale faces Princeton on the road on Friday. Dartmouth plays Columbia at home on Friday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
